<title>ITALY: CYCLING-SGAMBELLURI WINS SIXTH GIRO STAGE.</title>
<headline>CYCLING-SGAMBELLURI WINS SIXTH GIRO STAGE.</headline>
<dateline>LANCIANO, Italy 1997-05-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Roberto Sgambelluri of Italy won the 210-kms sixth stage of the Giro d'Italia cycle race on Thursday, according to provisional results.  </p>
<p>Dario Frigo of Italy was second and compatriot Michele Coppolillo third, according to provisional results.</p>
<p>Pavel Tonkov of Russia retained the overall race leader's pink jersey.</p>
